{"tid":912813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國或向棄用華為產品的國家提供財政援助","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T03:33:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f40d4b388d322698868da7dff7221b8aec663714","tid":912813,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1429738_1_20181123103507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1429738_1_20181123103507.jpg&h=dde8943d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》報道，華府正試圖說服盟友，避免使用中國華為的產品。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，德國、意大利及日本等，廣泛使用華為的設備。美國官員正將他們認為華為產品涉及的網絡安全風險，告知這些國家的官員、無線設備及互聯網供應商的管理層。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，美國在這些國家有軍事設施，憂慮當地的中國電訊設備，構成網絡保安漏洞，洩露敏感訊息，美國甚至考慮向棄用華為產品的國家，在電訊發展方面提供財政援助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429738-20181123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429738-20181123.htm&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=00bf9b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429738-20181123.htm&h=9b7ba55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429738-20181123.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0b45cc257e29f0c9056e140070c7fe4bd1dd0ca0","tid":912813,"uid":91403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"美國大撒幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a84d90fa4cecf3db48811c170fbe9545d21384d","tid":912813,"uid":84128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"美軍來了你帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />